         <t:div type="edition">
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="MainPart">
               <t:label>Main part</t:label>
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <t:ab>
                   በከመ፡ ይቤ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ይትፌሥሑ፡ አሕዛብ፡ በሰሚዐ፡ ዜናሆሙ፡ ለጻድቃን፡
                  </t:ab>
               </t:div>
               <t:div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <t:ab>
                     በመዋዕለ፡ አውግስጦስ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ዘሮሜ። ወበኢትዮጵያ፡ ሣህል፡ ንጉስ። ወእምዓመተ፡ ዲዮቅልጥያኖስ፡ በ፪፻፵ወ፮ዓመት።
                  </t:ab>
               </t:div>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Epilogue">
               <t:label>Epilogue</t:label>
               <t:ab>
                  ወዓለምክዋ፡ አነ፡ ይስሐቅ፡ <t:gap reason="omitted"/> ወአሜን።
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
